Packages
numerics.hyperbolics The numerics.hyperbolics class provides methods to calculate gamma functions and the modified Bessel function of the first kind [ bessel(X,V) ] for real values X & V.
roadway_dispersion The roadway_dispersion package contains the core routines of the UCD 2001 roadway dispersion model.
ucd_2001_fe The ucd_2001_fe package stores classes which constitutes a front end to the UCD_2001 Roadway Dispersion Model.
utilities The utilities class provides a number of routines that required by the UCD 2001 roadway dispersion model.
